cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.CR, cs.CC 

This paper focuses on the performance evaluation of virtual network functions (VNFs) on cloud instances, which falls under the category of networked and distributed systems (cs.NI). It also discusses the optimization of VNF instance selection and service chain provisioning, which can be categorized under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), systems and control (cs.SY), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
